{"tid":155482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日左叫雞.....","createTime":"2017-03-14T05:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T05:53:44.000Z","uid":37614,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a006e26c337f396cff1f3435ad485e6caba23169","tid":155482,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說今日有需求想叫下雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrY75H2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrY75H2.jpg&h=c588f046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就黎比錢果下<br />\n冇啦啦有個男人衝左過黎<br />\n我以為佢想打尖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎忍唔住打佢果陣<br />\n佢問收銀條友拎手套<br />\n咁我就放佢一馬啦<br />\n點知。。。<br />\n條友話手套冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽完之後<br />\n我再望望枱上面未比錢嘅兩舊雞<br />\n又唔好意思話唔要<br />\n唯有做死雞買左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加問題黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我舊雞點食好<br />\n利申：唔想用手"},{"pid":"15f992357ddd2e370826309e238d451534d435d9","tid":155482,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"咁幾時會右叫埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9507de27b7bb3e8495b27c11d9500215da67499","tid":155482,"uid":8447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"好似狗咁食"},{"pid":"8db0404878da5f5ff917034de76f2383ce1999b0","tid":155482,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"問職員拎刀叉, 即刻高人一等"},{"pid":"2818071a8230de06b66e3ea64b5d11fbeaf02b56","tid":155482,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"用紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c137b42245c2eb5d3908b2a450d9f2dcce3c13","tid":155482,"uid":8848,"li